headline: Assessing Blackstone (BX) Valuation After Earnings Beat And Growing Fee And AI Infrastructure Tailwinds
summary: Blackstone (BX) is back in focus after reporting full year 2025 results, with revenue of US$14,450.27 million and net income of US$3,019.21 million, alongside commentary on fee growth drivers. See our latest analysis for Blackstone.
